ÃDedicated to Benjamin & Johanna Johnstone
who gave their sons so that we may live in freedom
"They lie at peace now, their guns silent,
only we that are left fight the war of broken hearts."

Joseph Johnstone 1886-1917
Walter Johnstone 1890-1917
Ernest Johnstone 1898-1918
William Benjamin Johnstone 1896-1919
Sydney Johnstone 1900-1921
William George Johnstone 1889-1964

"Such a family is entitled to be remembered with
affectionate pride wherever the English language is spoken."
Unveiling of the monument 22nd December 1922

EDITH ANNIE THOMAS
01/08/1924 - 27/01/2018"„
